{
  "stem": "3097.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Farther, a Pole even couldn't go there, except those who lived there, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she came and told me about Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She told me that the people are being taken there to the camp, and nobody knows what happens to them, OK?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a cousin of Wasser, Joseph, Josel-- Josel Wasser, Joseph Wasser-- this size boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was about, maybe 14 or 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very short.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Went to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people in Treblinka took him and put him in a wagon with the clothes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Put him in the wagon and the clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he came towards our city, he made a hole in the-- in the wood and jumped out and came to our camp, to arbeitslager.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And told us the story about the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Told us a story about this wooden clock, OK?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And about killing machines, and about thousands of people coming daily, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody believed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The chief of the police [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Spiegel ?] said not to spread this kind of information, because it's not true.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I discussed the situation with Minsberg, I said, you know what they do with the people?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If it's true that they destroy them, they take the people on a field, and the [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stukas ?] come like during the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they kill the people that way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because who did imagine that there is something like you see, assembly line, killing people?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That they take-- take thousands of people, in one day, that they can destroy and-- and make ashes out of it?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We couldn't understand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we came to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
